                                    <watches>3</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16762190" author="mkarg" created="Wed, 6 Feb 2019 22:18:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also fails in 3.1.0-SNAPSHOT.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16762402" author="mkarg" created="Thu, 7 Feb 2019 06:16:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I assume this is caused by Maven Javadoc Plugin adding --module-path as soon as it finds a module-info.java file in the src folder. This should be modified in a way that the existence of that file is to be ignored by the plugin as soon as the provided &amp;lt;source&amp;gt; is 8 or older, because the aim of such a feature / files combination simply is to have JavaDocs created &quot;as if&quot; the used JDK &quot;would be&quot; 8 - and JDK 8&apos;s JavaDoc tool simply ignores that file.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16763563" author="rfscholte" created="Fri, 8 Feb 2019 12:54:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=maven-javadoc-plugin.git;a=commit;h=1fe0654bfe1ca550219f428c0dd767a3e70dab69&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;1fe0654bfe1ca550219f428c0dd767a3e70dab69&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16763578" author="hudson" created="Fri, 8 Feb 2019 13:14:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Build succeeded in Jenkins: Maven TLP &#187; maven-javadoc-plugin &#187; master #143&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/maven-box/job/maven-javadoc-plugin/job/master/143/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/maven-box/job/maven-javadoc-plugin/job/master/143/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17957963" author="olamy" created="Tue, 10 Jun 2025 05:09:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This project has moved from Jira to GitHub Issues. This issue was migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-javadoc-plugin/issues/873&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;apache/maven-javadoc-plugin#873&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
